    "OPEN": {
      "name": "OPEN_type_S_global_Mpad_and_highs_le_Kmax",
      "statement": "(1) Global Type S M_pad bound at free_core=846161: peel gives structure and free_core=2 through-pack, but full M_pad\u22642 needs controlling unions of through-sets / residual Type S absence.\n(2) |A_SP free-1 highs| \u2264 2176 (or constructive \u03ba into that range) for side marks.",
